name: A Song of Hex and Jynx - #2  Witches and Prayers.
description: The three sisters of witches ran away from their last village, after the tragedy they faced. In the running, they realised the magical and witchy night had arrived; the Halloween night. They went to the highest hill and saw a lot of other folks were celebrating the night with costumes and decorations, down there in some random town. Feeling the bliss was in the air, they couldn’t helped but prayed to mother nature for a better future, for the minds of normal folks became brighter and wider, so the fate of witches would no longer in danger.
